txt.en:
A swift swipe meant for the eyes. Breaks your opponent's concentration.

This skill will interrupt your target's inductions.

<rgb=#FF7700> 
 
 In Flayer: Eye Gash 
 Brute bonus: Decreases block, parry, and evade rating. 
 
 In Shadow: Eye Gouge 
 From stealth: Decreases range of targets ranged skills.  </rgb>
